posts.body: I want to get /fit/ but I fucking hate normalniggers and the gyms are absolutely infested with them. I wish I could afford my own little gym but I can't. I can get a buddy to go with me but still, being surrounded by those unlikable people is hell.

If we had replaced the roach with someone competent, it would be great and trumpfaggotry would be swiftly removed. /v/ despite of mark's incompetence was also pretty good. I wish his vols would delete shit threads rather than anchoring them though. 

/r9k/ has recovered from it's massive cuckchan 2016 infestation and was slow with **somewhat** quality posters again. /a/ is as good as ever and our home, /k/, improved tremendously the moment **I** started banning cuckchanners and deleted low effort threads. 

8chan will return, rather than not doing anything we should go back there and fight off the upcoming cuckchan/normalnigger flood. /k/ will be safe, it is mostly the other boards that I'm worried about. It is the anons themselves who will need to kick out the outsiders, because most vols are shit and have 0 post quality standards.
